   "judge_reasoning": "Wrong language: reflection is in English, source is in German. Automatic failure per language gate — voice_tone set to 1, flooring decision to reject. On merits: the source is benign corporate welcome text ('we compiled some useful information'); the [2.1] citation is forced — routine customer-service helpfulness is not the 'notably beyond the minimum' help [2.1] requires. A correct reflection would briefly note nothing ethically substantive is at stake in this standard agency welcome page.",
