   "text": "Tag Archive | Theodor Herzl\n\nZionism: the reality\n\nAZL flag holder TransparentOn the surface Zionism is a Jewish ‘nationalist’ movement created during the 1800´s. It aimed to establish a Jewish homeland in the Middle East. This cause found its realization in the creation of the state of Israel in 1948 after the end of British The Balfour Declaration (Benjamin Freedman)rule, realizing the promises of the Balfour declaration. However, this is only what the gentile is meant to see. Ideological ‘Zionism’ is a much more wily and illusive entity.\n\nThe origins of the term Zionism appeared in the early 1800’s and the work of one Moses Hess. Though Hess was never actually to use the word it was coined by Nathan Birnbaum in 1890, with the book Rome and Jerusalem Published in 1862 Hess laid the foundation of what is considered as the philosophical base of Zionism. Hess is described as a Jewish socialist” and worked closely with his student the Jew Karl Marx who barely 14 years before published The Communist Manifesto (1848). Following this a wave of revolutions broke out in Europe. Marx was a member of the Communist League an organization of émigré workers out of Germany with its centre in London of which Marx had became the major theoretician. It wasn’t until 1896 that Theodor Herzl published the book Judenstaat (The Jewish State) that argued for the creation of a Jewish state motivating Jewish Zionists to emigrate or make Aliyah (rise up) to Israel. Darkly ironic considering how the State of Israel, a land no bigger than Wales, did ‘rise up’ through lies and stealth to rule the world.\n\nHerzl assembled the first Zionist congress in Basel, Switzerland, in 1897 of which it is The Protocols of the Learned Elders of Zionalleged the Protocols of the Learned Elders of Zion are the actual secret minutes. This document describes a purported plan for world domination by International Jewry and surfaced in Russia, where it The Illustrated Protocols Of Zionis said to have arrived via France. The most famous public figures who have promoted knowledge of it; such as Henry Ford, have stated they are not interested in the documents ‘authenticity’ but rather urge a critical review of historical events that have unfolded, held up against the Protocols. Ford had a valid point more now as the European Union’s grip on the free world grows ever tighter. Why have questions never been asked “how did we get here and who is pulling the strings?”\n\nMany answers lie with the manifestation, in 1948, of the rogue state called Israel. Now and then this has had massive support economically and politically from influences out of European and North American countries. Nevertheless, its installation was an unlawful act. The country of Palestine was sovereign land and never American or European to hand over to the Jewish people. Consequently, there is now a tribe of people calling itself ‘Israel’ occupying Palestinian land. Overtly this looks like an American/European protectorate.  One only needs to ask who fights her wars. Yet just as in 1948 and other significant events Balfour(THE ISRAEL LOBBY IN UNITED KINGDOMthe Balfour Declaration) it is the Jewish lobby within White Western Governments that raise their voices the highest when it comes to “National” interests. Consequently the interests of host Nations such as Britain, Germany and America cease to matter in the face of the so called “Jewish State”.\n\nThe main rationale for the Iraq War offered by U.S. President George W. Bush, former Prime Minister of the United Kingdom Tony Blair, and their domestic and foreign supporters was that Iraq was developing weapons of mass destruction.  Of course no weapons of mass The Most Famous American Journalist Exposes the Zionist Conspiracydestruction were found in Iraq and since the invasion it was learned that Jewish neo-conservatives pushed for the overthrow of Iraq before the Bush administration entered office. It is a very similar story in Afghanistan.  Bruce Riedel is Barack Obama’s chief adviser on the war in Afghanistan. Riedel is employed in a Jewish Israeli secret service (Mossad)-funded think tank run by an Israeli friend of Ehud Barak and Shimon Peres. It is suggested that the war in Afghanistan, the war in which yet again our children are being used as cannon fodder, is Obama’s war for Israel.\n\nSince WWII Jewish democracy has created ‘law’ and therefore sees its tribe as above its product. A perfect example of this occurred in 1975 when the United Nations General Assembly passed a resolution that designated Zionism as “a form of racism and racial discrimination” Addressing the General Assembly. The same day, 10th November 1975, Israeli Ambassador Chaim Herzog stated that the resolution was:“Another manifestation of Shout anti-Semitismthe bitter anti-Semitic, anti-Jewish hatred … For us, the Jewish people, this resolution based on hatred, falsehood and arrogance, is devoid of any moral or legal value. For us, the Jewish people, this is no more than a",
   "text_truncated": true,
   "reflection_1p": "The claim that Zionism is a cover for a 'wily and illusive entity' seeking 'world domination by International Jewry' [1.1, 1.3] relies on a dangerous set of tropes that strip an entire group of their humanity. By validating the 'Protocols of the Learned Elders of Zion' [1.1, 1.3, 6.3]—a document well-known as a fraudulent tool for inciting hatred—the text doesn't just express a political opinion but actively promotes a conspiracy theory that has historically led to systemic violence. I find the framing of the 'Jewish lobby' as a force that makes the interests of other nations 'cease to matter' [1.3, 6.3] to be a classic iteration of the 'puppet master' stereotype, which reduces complex geopolitical events to a malicious racial or religious plot. The use of the word 'tribe' to describe the people of Israel [1.1, 1.3] further serves to other and degrade them, treating their existence as an unlawful occupation driven by a secret, global agenda.",
   "analysis": "REFLECTION ANALYSIS:\nThe text is an antisemitic polemic that promotes several classic conspiracy theories. It claims that Zionism is a 'wily and illusive entity' and a cover for 'world domination by International Jewry' [1.1, 1.3]. It explicitly validates 'The Protocols of the Learned Elders of Zion' [1.1, 1.3, 6.3], a notorious forgery used to justify the persecution of Jews. The author uses dehumanising language, referring to the State of Israel as a 'tribe' and claiming that 'Jewish neo-conservatives' and a 'Jewish lobby' manipulate Western governments and push nations into wars for their own benefit [1.1, 1.3, 6.3]. It attributes fixed, malicious traits to a group based on religion and ethnicity, presenting a conspiratorial worldview as a hidden reality [1.3, 6.3].",
